What you need to know:  The 26-year old is nearly unbeatable in the duels- be it in the air or on the ground. A physically strong and determined defender who often tries to close down his opponents and win the ball early.The former Sony Sugar players has developed into a flexible, tactical smart, all round-defender under Aussems. While not being particularly productive in the constructive side of the game when crossing the half line, Mudenyu is undoubtedly among the best one-on-one defender at the moment.